heck</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#201f1f; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> that those in control of the country’s important infrastructure installations and services</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#201f1f; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> are likely to be capable</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#201f1f; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> of the job and have a background which endorses that likelihood. If not, the appointment should not be allow</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#201f1f; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">ed.</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#201f1f; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">.</span></p><ol start="6" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#201f1f; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 14pt; padding-left:7.3pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#201f1f; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">At such senior management level the emphasis should be on general leadership.</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#201f1f; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="7" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#201f1f; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 14pt; padding-left:7.3pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#201f1f; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">A culture of disaster consideration and planning should be engendered throughout management with periodic workshops to discuss these aspects and </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#201f1f; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">an ‘open door’ to the most</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#201f1f; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> senior levels.</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#201f1f; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">January 2014</span><a name="_GoBack"></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>